<div class="language-math line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="math"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">$$J(\theta) = \frac{1}{2m}\sum_{i = 0} ^m(y^i - h_\theta (x^i))^2$$</span>
